{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe012358cb","title":"在中共中央政治局会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e1b0175d48","index":0,"year":1946,"month":2,"day":12,"articleId":"fe012358cb"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e20a0fc60c","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局会议上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fe012358cb"},{"id":"4c53970775","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年2月12日）美国和将介石要以全国军队统一来消灭我们，我们要统一而不被消灭。军党分立还不是最危险的，合编分驻才是最危险的。杂牌年还没有与蒋介石的嫩系部队合编的，连杂牌的集团军都没有与蒋介石婧系部队参杂合编。我们现在只有对付好，才能摆脱危险。全国军队统一，原则上我们只好赞成，实行步骤要看具体情况，这是我们与法国不同的。[1]这是毛泽东在中共中央政治局会议上关于同国民党谈判整年方案问","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fe012358cb"}],"page":{"id":"18c8c173c5","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"fe012358cb","start":179,"end":179}}}},"__N_SSG":true}